formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1) Estimated Cost is as certified by the Management
2) Actual Cost incurred is taken from the unaudited provisional books of accounts
3) Based on the information provided by the management, Annexure A has been divided into two different tables, wherein the 11 plots shown in Table - 2 were booked/reserved/sold by Pruthvi Co Operative Housing Society Limited Vibhag 3 / Previous developer . The books of accounts of Deepspace Properties LLP do not take into consideration the Costs and Sales of the 11 plots. However, as these plots form part of the overall project "129 Retreat", thus information regarding these plots have been shown as part of Annexure A. 								
4) Deposit / Withdrawals for others includes transaction of Fixed deposit from RERA bank account, interest earn on the Fixed deposits, return of money on cancellation of unit etc.
5) In some units the promoter had executed sale deed before getting registered under RERA and therefore we have considered these sale deed and have mentioned its date of execution in Form 3A.	
6) The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility
includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement,
and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances.
7) The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project solely for the purpose to enable comply with
requirement of RERA , and should not be used by any other person or for any other purpose. Accordingly, we do not accept or
assume any liability or any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into
whose hands it may come without our prior consent in writing.
8) The details mentioned in Annexure A such as carpet area, booking status, unit consideration, date of agreement to sale,
encumbrance status, name, KYC and mobile numbers of allottees are as provided by the management. Received amount has
been verified with the books of accounts
